DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Audit] USING (

(@p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, 1),
(@p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, 2),
(@p24, @p25, @p26, @p27, @p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, 3),
(@p32, @p33, @p34, @p35, @p36, @p37, @p38, @p39, 4),
(@p40, @p41, @p42, @p43, @p44, @p45, @p46, @p47, 5),
(@p48, @p49, @p50, @p51, @p52, @p53, @p54, @p55, 6),
(@p56, @p57, @p58, @p59, @p60, @p61, @p62, @p63, 7),

(@p72, @p73, @p74, @p75, @p76, @p77, @p78, @p79, 9)) AS i ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN

VALUES (i.[AffectedColumns], i.[DateTime], i.[NewValues], i.[OldValues], i.[PrimaryKey], i.[TableName], i.[Type], i.[UserId])

INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [Audit] t
INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted10 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [InsurerBranch] USING (
VALUES (@p80, @p81, @p82, @p83, @p84, @p85, @p86, @p87, @p88, @p89, @p90, @p91, 0)) AS i ([AddedBy], [CityId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [Fax], [InsurerId], [IsPrimary], [ModifiedBy], [Name], [Phone], [PhysicalAddress], [PostalAddress], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN

INNER JOIN @inserted10 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])

MERGE [PortfolioClient] USING (
VALUES (@p92, @p93, @p94, @p95, @p96, @p97, @p98, @p99, 0),

OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[AddedBy], [t].[DateAdded], [t].[DateModified], [t].[ModifiedBy], [t].[Name], [t].[TaxDate], [t].[TaxRate]
FROM [Tax] AS [t]
ORDER BY [t].[TaxDate] DESC

SELECT TOP(1) [i].[Id], [i].[AddedBy], [i].[CityId], [i].[DateAdded], [i].[DateModified], [i].[Fax], [i].[InsurerId], [i].[IsPrimary], [i].[ModifiedBy], [i].[Name], [i].[Phone], [i].[PhysicalAddress], [i].[PostalAddress]
FROM [InsurerBranch] AS [i]
WHERE [i].[Name] = N'No Insurer Branch'

SET NOCOUNT ON;
DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Audit] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, 0),
(@p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, 1),
(@p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, 2),
(@p24, @p25, @p26, @p27, @p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, 3),
(@p32, @p33, @p34, @p35, @p36, @p37, @p38, @p39, 4),
(@p40, @p41, @p42, @p43, @p44, @p45, @p46, @p47, 5),
(@p48, @p49, @p50, @p51, @p52, @p53, @p54, @p55, 6),
(@p56, @p57, @p58, @p59, @p60, @p61, @p62, @p63, 7),
(@p64, @p65, @p66, @p67, @p68, @p69, @p70, @p71, 8),
(@p72, @p73, @p74, @p75, @p76, @p77, @p78, @p79, 9)) AS i ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId])
VALUES (i.[AffectedColumns], i.[DateTime], i.[NewValues], i.[OldValues], i.[PrimaryKey], i.[TableName], i.[Type], i.[UserId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [Audit] t
INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted10 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [InsurerBranch] USING (
VALUES (@p80, @p81, @p82, @p83, @p84, @p85, @p86, @p87, @p88, @p89, @p90, @p91, 0)) AS i ([AddedBy], [CityId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [Fax], [InsurerId], [IsPrimary], [ModifiedBy], [Name], [Phone], [PhysicalAddress], [PostalAddress], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddedBy], [CityId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [Fax], [InsurerId], [IsPrimary], [ModifiedBy], [Name], [Phone], [PhysicalAddress], [PostalAddress])
VALUES (i.[AddedBy], i.[CityId], i.[DateAdded], i.[DateModified], i.[Fax], i.[InsurerId], i.[IsPrimary], i.[ModifiedBy], i.[Name], i.[Phone], i.[PhysicalAddress], i.[PostalAddress])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted10;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [InsurerBranch] t
INNER JOIN @inserted10 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted11 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [PortfolioClient] USING (
VALUES (@p92, @p93, @p94, @p95, @p96, @p97, @p98, @p99, 0),
(@p100, @p101, @p102, @p103, @p104, @p105, @p106, @p107, 1)) AS i ([AddedById], [ClientId], [ClientStatusId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [IsWithdrawal], [ModifiedById], [PortfolioId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddedById], [ClientId], [ClientStatusId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [IsWithdrawal], [ModifiedById], [PortfolioId])
VALUES (i.[AddedById], i.[ClientId], i.[ClientStatusId], i.[DateAdded], i.[DateModified], i.[IsWithdrawal], i.[ModifiedById], i.[PortfolioId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted11;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [PortfolioClient] t
INNER JOIN @inserted11 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

(@p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, 2),
(@p24, @p25, @p26, @p27, @p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, 3),
(@p32, @p33, @p34, @p35, @p36, @p37, @p38, @p39, 4),

FROM [Tax] AS [t]
ORDER BY [t].[TaxDate] DESC

SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[AddedBy], [i].[CityId], [i].[DateAdded], [i].[DateModified], [i].[Fax], [i].[InsurerId], [i].[IsPrimary], [i].[ModifiedBy], [i].[Name], [i].[Phone], [i].[PhysicalAddress], [i].[PostalAddress]
FROM [InsurerBranch] AS [i]
WHERE [i].[Name] = N'No Insurer Branch'
ORDER BY [i].[Name] DESC

SET NOCOUNT ON;
DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Audit] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, 0),
(@p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, 1),
(@p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, 2),
(@p24, @p25, @p26, @p27, @p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, 3),
(@p32, @p33, @p34, @p35, @p36, @p37, @p38, @p39, 4),
(@p40, @p41, @p42, @p43, @p44, @p45, @p46, @p47, 5),
(@p48, @p49, @p50, @p51, @p52, @p53, @p54, @p55, 6),
(@p56, @p57, @p58, @p59, @p60, @p61, @p62, @p63, 7),
(@p64, @p65, @p66, @p67, @p68, @p69, @p70, @p71, 8),
(@p72, @p73, @p74, @p75, @p76, @p77, @p78, @p79, 9)) AS i ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId])
VALUES (i.[AffectedColumns], i.[DateTime], i.[NewValues], i.[OldValues], i.[PrimaryKey], i.[TableName], i.[Type], i.[UserId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [Audit] t
INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted10 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [InsurerBranch] USING (
VALUES (@p80, @p81, @p82, @p83, @p84, @p85, @p86, @p87, @p88, @p89, @p90, @p91, 0)) AS i ([AddedBy], [CityId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [Fax], [InsurerId], [IsPrimary], [ModifiedBy], [Name], [Phone], [PhysicalAddress], [PostalAddress], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddedBy], [CityId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [Fax], [InsurerId], [IsPrimary], [ModifiedBy], [Name], [Phone], [PhysicalAddress], [PostalAddress])
VALUES (i.[AddedBy], i.[CityId], i.[DateAdded], i.[DateModified], i.[Fax], i.[InsurerId], i.[IsPrimary], i.[ModifiedBy], i.[Name], i.[Phone], i.[PhysicalAddress], i.[PostalAddress])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position

ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted11 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [PortfolioClient] USING (
VALUES (@p92, @p93, @p94, @p95, @p96, @p97, @p98, @p99, 0),
(@p100, @p101, @p102, @p103, @p104, @p105, @p106, @p107, 1)) AS i ([AddedById], [ClientId], [ClientStatusId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [IsWithdrawal], [ModifiedById], [PortfolioId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddedById], [ClientId], [ClientStatusId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [IsWithdrawal], [ModifiedById], [PortfolioId])
VALUES (i.[AddedById], i.[ClientId], i.[ClientStatusId], i.[DateAdded], i.[DateModified], i.[IsWithdrawal], i.[ModifiedById], i.[PortfolioId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted11;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [PortfolioClient] t
INNER JOIN @inserted11 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

SET NOCOUNT ON;
DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Audit] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, 0),
(@p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, 1),
(@p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, 2),
(@p24, @p25, @p26, @p27, @p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, 3),
(@p32, @p33, @p34, @p35, @p36, @p37, @p38, @p39, 4),
(@p40, @p41, @p42, @p43, @p44, @p45, @p46, @p47, 5),
(@p48, @p49, @p50, @p51, @p52, @p53, @p54, @p55, 6),
(@p56, @p57, @p58, @p59, @p60, @p61, @p62, @p63, 7),
(@p64, @p65, @p66, @p67, @p68, @p69, @p70, @p71, 8),
(@p72, @p73, @p74, @p75, @p76, @p77, @p78, @p79, 9)) AS i ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId])
VALUES (i.[AffectedColumns], i.[DateTime], i.[NewValues], i.[OldValues], i.[PrimaryKey], i.[TableName], i.[Type], i.[UserId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [Audit] t
INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted10 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [InsurerBranch] USING (
VALUES (@p80, @p81, @p82, @p83, @p84, @p85, @p86, @p87, @p88, @p89, @p90, @p91, 0)) AS i ([AddedBy], [CityId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [Fax], [InsurerId], [IsPrimary], [ModifiedBy], [Name], [Phone], [PhysicalAddress], [PostalAddress], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddedBy], [CityId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [Fax], [InsurerId], [IsPrimary], [ModifiedBy], [Name], [Phone], [PhysicalAddress], [PostalAddress])
VALUES (i.[AddedBy], i.[CityId], i.[DateAdded], i.[DateModified], i.[Fax], i.[InsurerId], i.[IsPrimary], i.[ModifiedBy], i.[Name], i.[Phone], i.[PhysicalAddress], i.[PostalAddress])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted10;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [InsurerBranch] t
INNER JOIN @inserted10 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted11 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [PortfolioClient] USING (
VALUES (@p92, @p93, @p94, @p95, @p96, @p97, @p98, @p99, 0),
(@p100, @p101, @p102, @p103, @p104, @p105, @p106, @p107, 1)) AS i ([AddedById], [ClientId], [ClientStatusId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [IsWithdrawal], [ModifiedById], [PortfolioId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddedById], [ClientId], [ClientStatusId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [IsWithdrawal], [ModifiedById], [PortfolioId])
VALUES (i.[AddedById], i.[ClientId], i.[ClientStatusId], i.[DateAdded], i.[DateModified], i.[IsWithdrawal], i.[ModifiedById], i.[PortfolioId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted11;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [PortfolioClient] t
INNER JOIN @inserted11 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[AddedBy], [t].[DateAdded], [t].[DateModified], [t].[ModifiedBy], [t].[Name], [t].[TaxDate], [t].[TaxRate]
FROM [Tax] AS [t]
ORDER BY [t].[TaxDate] DESC

SELECT TOP(1) [i].[Id], [i].[AddedBy], [i].[CityId], [i].[DateAdded], [i].[DateModified], [i].[Fax], [i].[InsurerId], [i].[IsPrimary], [i].[ModifiedBy], [i].[Name], [i].[Phone], [i].[PhysicalAddress], [i].[PostalAddress]
FROM [InsurerBranch] AS [i]
WHERE [i].[Name] = N'No Insurer Branch'

SET NOCOUNT ON;
DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Audit] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, 0),
(@p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, 1),
(@p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, 2),
(@p24, @p25, @p26, @p27, @p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, 3),
(@p32, @p33, @p34, @p35, @p36, @p37, @p38, @p39, 4),
(@p40, @p41, @p42, @p43, @p44, @p45, @p46, @p47, 5),
(@p48, @p49, @p50, @p51, @p52, @p53, @p54, @p55, 6),
(@p56, @p57, @p58, @p59, @p60, @p61, @p62, @p63, 7),
(@p64, @p65, @p66, @p67, @p68, @p69, @p70, @p71, 8),
(@p72, @p73, @p74, @p75, @p76, @p77, @p78, @p79, 9)) AS i ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId])
VALUES (i.[AffectedColumns], i.[DateTime], i.[NewValues], i.[OldValues], i.[PrimaryKey], i.[TableName], i.[Type], i.[UserId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [Audit] t
INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted10 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [InsurerBranch] USING (
VALUES (@p80, @p81, @p82, @p83, @p84, @p85, @p86, @p87, @p88, @p89, @p90, @p91, 0)) AS i ([AddedBy], [CityId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [Fax], [InsurerId], [IsPrimary], [ModifiedBy], [Name], [Phone], [PhysicalAddress], [PostalAddress], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddedBy], [CityId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [Fax], [InsurerId], [IsPrimary], [ModifiedBy], [Name], [Phone], [PhysicalAddress], [PostalAddress])
VALUES (i.[AddedBy], i.[CityId], i.[DateAdded], i.[DateModified], i.[Fax], i.[InsurerId], i.[IsPrimary], i.[ModifiedBy], i.[Name], i.[Phone], i.[PhysicalAddress], i.[PostalAddress])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted10;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [InsurerBranch] t
INNER JOIN @inserted10 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted11 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [PortfolioClient] USING (
VALUES (@p92, @p93, @p94, @p95, @p96, @p97, @p98, @p99, 0),
(@p100, @p101, @p102, @p103, @p104, @p105, @p106, @p107, 1)) AS i ([AddedById], [ClientId], [ClientStatusId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [IsWithdrawal], [ModifiedById], [PortfolioId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddedById], [ClientId], [ClientStatusId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [IsWithdrawal], [ModifiedById], [PortfolioId])
VALUES (i.[AddedById], i.[ClientId], i.[ClientStatusId], i.[DateAdded], i.[DateModified], i.[IsWithdrawal], i.[ModifiedById], i.[PortfolioId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted11;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [PortfolioClient] t
INNER JOIN @inserted11 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Audit] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, 0),
(@p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, 1),
(@p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, 2),
(@p24, @p25, @p26, @p27, @p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, 3),
(@p32, @p33, @p34, @p35, @p36, @p37, @p38, @p39, 4),
(@p40, @p41, @p42, @p43, @p44, @p45, @p46, @p47, 5),
(@p48, @p49, @p50, @p51, @p52, @p53, @p54, @p55, 6),

WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId])
VALUES (i.[AffectedColumns], i.[DateTime], i.[NewValues], i.[OldValues], i.[PrimaryKey], i.[TableName], i.[Type], i.[UserId])

INTO @inserted0;

SET NOCOUNT ON;
DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Audit] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, 0),
(@p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, 1),
(@p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, 2),
(@p24, @p25, @p26, @p27, @p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, 3),
(@p32, @p33, @p34, @p35, @p36, @p37, @p38, @p39, 4),
(@p40, @p41, @p42, @p43, @p44, @p45, @p46, @p47, 5),
(@p48, @p49, @p50, @p51, @p52, @p53, @p54, @p55, 6),
(@p56, @p57, @p58, @p59, @p60, @p61, @p62, @p63, 7),
(@p64, @p65, @p66, @p67, @p68, @p69, @p70, @p71, 8),
(@p72, @p73, @p74, @p75, @p76, @p77, @p78, @p79, 9)) AS i ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId])
VALUES (i.[AffectedColumns], i.[DateTime], i.[NewValues], i.[OldValues], i.[PrimaryKey], i.[TableName], i.[Type], i.[UserId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [Audit] t
INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted10 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [InsurerBranch] USING (
VALUES (@p80, @p81, @p82, @p83, @p84, @p85, @p86, @p87, @p88, @p89, @p90, @p91, 0)) AS i ([AddedBy], [CityId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [Fax], [InsurerId], [IsPrimary], [ModifiedBy], [Name], [Phone], [PhysicalAddress], [PostalAddress], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddedBy], [CityId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [Fax], [InsurerId], [IsPrimary], [ModifiedBy], [Name], [Phone], [PhysicalAddress], [PostalAddress])
VALUES (i.[AddedBy], i.[CityId], i.[DateAdded], i.[DateModified], i.[Fax], i.[InsurerId], i.[IsPrimary], i.[ModifiedBy], i.[Name], i.[Phone], i.[PhysicalAddress], i.[PostalAddress])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted10;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [InsurerBranch] t
INNER JOIN @inserted10 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted11 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [PortfolioClient] USING (
VALUES (@p92, @p93, @p94, @p95, @p96, @p97, @p98, @p99, 0),
(@p100, @p101, @p102, @p103, @p104, @p105, @p106, @p107, 1)) AS i ([AddedById], [ClientId], [ClientStatusId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [IsWithdrawal], [ModifiedById], [PortfolioId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddedById], [ClientId], [ClientStatusId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [IsWithdrawal], [ModifiedById], [PortfolioId])
VALUES (i.[AddedById], i.[ClientId], i.[ClientStatusId], i.[DateAdded], i.[DateModified], i.[IsWithdrawal], i.[ModifiedById], i.[PortfolioId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted11;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [PortfolioClient] t

ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

SET NOCOUNT ON;
DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Audit] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, 0),
(@p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, 1),
(@p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, 2),
(@p24, @p25, @p26, @p27, @p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, 3),
(@p32, @p33, @p34, @p35, @p36, @p37, @p38, @p39, 4),
(@p40, @p41, @p42, @p43, @p44, @p45, @p46, @p47, 5),
(@p48, @p49, @p50, @p51, @p52, @p53, @p54, @p55, 6),
(@p56, @p57, @p58, @p59, @p60, @p61, @p62, @p63, 7),
(@p64, @p65, @p66, @p67, @p68, @p69, @p70, @p71, 8),
(@p72, @p73, @p74, @p75, @p76, @p77, @p78, @p79, 9)) AS i ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId])
VALUES (i.[AffectedColumns], i.[DateTime], i.[NewValues], i.[OldValues], i.[PrimaryKey], i.[TableName], i.[Type], i.[UserId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [Audit] t
INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted10 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [InsurerBranch] USING (
VALUES (@p80, @p81, @p82, @p83, @p84, @p85, @p86, @p87, @p88, @p89, @p90, @p91, 0)) AS i ([AddedBy], [CityId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [Fax], [InsurerId], [IsPrimary], [ModifiedBy], [Name], [Phone], [PhysicalAddress], [PostalAddress], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddedBy], [CityId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [Fax], [InsurerId], [IsPrimary], [ModifiedBy], [Name], [Phone], [PhysicalAddress], [PostalAddress])
VALUES (i.[AddedBy], i.[CityId], i.[DateAdded], i.[DateModified], i.[Fax], i.[InsurerId], i.[IsPrimary], i.[ModifiedBy], i.[Name], i.[Phone], i.[PhysicalAddress], i.[PostalAddress])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted10;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [InsurerBranch] t
INNER JOIN @inserted10 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted11 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [PortfolioClient] USING (
VALUES (@p92, @p93, @p94, @p95, @p96, @p97, @p98, @p99, 0),
(@p100, @p101, @p102, @p103, @p104, @p105, @p106, @p107, 1)) AS i ([AddedById], [ClientId], [ClientStatusId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [IsWithdrawal], [ModifiedById], [PortfolioId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddedById], [ClientId], [ClientStatusId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [IsWithdrawal], [ModifiedById], [PortfolioId])
VALUES (i.[AddedById], i.[ClientId], i.[ClientStatusId], i.[DateAdded], i.[DateModified], i.[IsWithdrawal], i.[ModifiedById], i.[PortfolioId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted11;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [PortfolioClient] t

ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

FROM [Tax] AS [t]
ORDER BY [t].[TaxDate] DESC

SELECT TOP(1) [i].[Id], [i].[AddedBy], [i].[CityId], [i].[DateAdded], [i].[DateModified], [i].[Fax], [i].[InsurerId], [i].[IsPrimary], [i].[ModifiedBy], [i].[Name], [i].[Phone], [i].[PhysicalAddress], [i].[PostalAddress]
FROM [InsurerBranch] AS [i]
WHERE [i].[Name] = N'No Insurer Branch'

SET NOCOUNT ON;
DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Audit] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, 0),
(@p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, 1),
(@p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, 2),
(@p24, @p25, @p26, @p27, @p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, 3),
(@p32, @p33, @p34, @p35, @p36, @p37, @p38, @p39, 4),
(@p40, @p41, @p42, @p43, @p44, @p45, @p46, @p47, 5),
(@p48, @p49, @p50, @p51, @p52, @p53, @p54, @p55, 6),
(@p56, @p57, @p58, @p59, @p60, @p61, @p62, @p63, 7),
(@p64, @p65, @p66, @p67, @p68, @p69, @p70, @p71, 8),
(@p72, @p73, @p74, @p75, @p76, @p77, @p78, @p79, 9)) AS i ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId])
VALUES (i.[AffectedColumns], i.[DateTime], i.[NewValues], i.[OldValues], i.[PrimaryKey], i.[TableName], i.[Type], i.[UserId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [Audit] t
INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted10 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [InsurerBranch] USING (
VALUES (@p80, @p81, @p82, @p83, @p84, @p85, @p86, @p87, @p88, @p89, @p90, @p91, 0)) AS i ([AddedBy], [CityId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [Fax], [InsurerId], [IsPrimary], [ModifiedBy], [Name], [Phone], [PhysicalAddress], [PostalAddress], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddedBy], [CityId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [Fax], [InsurerId], [IsPrimary], [ModifiedBy], [Name], [Phone], [PhysicalAddress], [PostalAddress])
VALUES (i.[AddedBy], i.[CityId], i.[DateAdded], i.[DateModified], i.[Fax], i.[InsurerId], i.[IsPrimary], i.[ModifiedBy], i.[Name], i.[Phone], i.[PhysicalAddress], i.[PostalAddress])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted10;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [InsurerBranch] t
INNER JOIN @inserted10 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

DECLARE @inserted11 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [PortfolioClient] USING (
VALUES (@p92, @p93, @p94, @p95, @p96, @p97, @p98, @p99, 0),
(@p100, @p101, @p102, @p103, @p104, @p105, @p106, @p107, 1)) AS i ([AddedById], [ClientId], [ClientStatusId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [IsWithdrawal], [ModifiedById], [PortfolioId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddedById], [ClientId], [ClientStatusId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [IsWithdrawal], [ModifiedById], [PortfolioId])
VALUES (i.[AddedById], i.[ClientId], i.[ClientStatusId], i.[DateAdded], i.[DateModified], i.[IsWithdrawal], i.[ModifiedById], i.[PortfolioId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted11;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [PortfolioClient] t
INNER JOIN @inserted11 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];
